videos.description: Kahlil Whitney looks for a teammate to pass to, then decides to hit a 3-pointer with a defender in his face.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Whitney assesses his options, then buries a triple) 2019/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Whitney assesses his options, then buries a triple

videos.description: K.J. Riley heaves up a trey with the shot clock dwindling down and gets it to go off the glass.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Evansville’s Riley banks a 3 with the shot clock winding down) 2019/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evansville's Riley banks a 3 with the shot clock winding down

videos.description: Kentucky freshman Tyrese Maxey takes the open baseline to the basket for an up-and-under layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Maxey cruises baseline for up-and-under layup) 2019/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maxey cruises baseline for up-and-under layup

videos.description: Kentucky freshman Tyrese Maxey tries to tie the game with a deep 3-pointer, but his attempt falls way short as Evansville upsets the No. 1 Wildcats.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kentucky taken down after Maxey's 3-pointer falls short) 2019/11/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kentucky taken down after Maxey's 3-pointer falls short

videos.description: Evansville douses head coach Walter McCarty with liquid in the locker room after its massive upset against No. 1 Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Misc. (Evansville celebrates big upset in the locker room) 2019/11/12

videos.headline: Evansville celebrates big upset in the locker room
